ENTRY            F1544   20260122   20260305   20260305       F106
SUBENT        F1544001   20260122   20260305   20260305       F106
BIB                 12         24
TITLE      Emission of high-energy 4He and 6,7Li nuclei in
           nuclear reaction of 56Fe ions on 238U target
AUTHOR     (V.A.Maslov,S.M.Lukyanov,V.V.Samarin,
           Yu.E.Penionzhkevich,M.A.Naumenko)
INSTITUTE  (4ZZZDUB,4RUSDBU,4RUSMIF)
REFERENCE  (J,BAS,89,1195,2025)
           #doi:10.1134/S1062873825711924
           (J,IZV,89,1180,2025) Russian original
REL-REF    (O,,Yu.E.Penionzhkevich+,J,PAN,85,145,2022) Energy
           spectra of He-4, Li-6 and Li-7 in 238U+56Fe reaction
           are given.
FACILITY   (ISOCY,4ZZZDUB) U400-M
INC-SOURCE The size of the 56Fe ion beam on the target was 5x5 mm2
           with the intensity of 100 nA.
METHOD     (EDE)
DETECTOR   (MAGSP) High-resolution magnetic spectrometer MAVR
           was used.
           (TELES,SI) Three semiconductor silicon telescopes
           with detectors deltaE1, deltaE2, and E of thicknesses
           50, 700, and 3200 mu-m, respectively, were used.
SAMPLE     The 238U target with a thickness of 1 mu-m was used.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No source of uncertainty is given.
HISTORY    (20260122R) Data were received from Dr. V.A. Maslov.
           (20260122C)
ENDBIB              24
COMMON               2          3
EN         ANG
MEV        ADEG
       400.         0.
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           31
